{"tid":1027912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"情侶性愛過激   啪到一半突然「卡」住  進退不能","createTime":"2019-02-19T06:22:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T17:06:05.000Z","uid":55851,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1e6a81d3cc80c5955fbf93cf8c696b42966d8d08","tid":1027912,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:22:34.000Z","msg":"剛果一對同姓戀人日前在家裡「翻雲覆雨」，沒想到2人在家裡激戰時，陽具卻剛好「卡住」拔不出來，激烈的疼痛讓雙方都痛不欲生，最後只好報警求援，而鄰居得知此事後也紛紛到場「參觀」，目擊者甚至將過程拍成影片放至網路，引起熱議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/02/18/1787215-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F02%2F18%2F1787215-XXL.jpg&h=77d11fe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲男子「啪」到一半突然卡住。（圖／翻攝自Anaedo Voice YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，此對戀人恩愛到一半疑似因為「被插入」的男子肛門肌痙攣，短髮男子陽具剛好卡住，雙方因此痛苦得不知如何是好，只好用床單圍住雙方下體再報警求救。影片中可看到，在屋內有許多男子包圍著2人討論該怎麼辦，長髮男子則痛到不斷搖晃，試圖減緩疼痛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/02/18/1787217-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F02%2F18%2F1787217-XXL.jpg&h=9bea817b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲2名男子舉步維艱。（圖／翻攝自Anaedo Voice YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n之後雙方起身走路，準備搭乘汽車就醫時，長髮男子仍痛得不斷彎腰、哀嚎，短髮男子還痛到翻白眼，露出一副欲哭無淚的神情，甚至還舉起雙手痛罵老天爺讓他發生這種事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/j3TIbuE-kkc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fj3TIbuE-kkc&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEgx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=a2e0746d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/j3TIbuE-kkc</a>"},{"pid":"74ea7537f62e9f248d0b154e14a560b3546f7d3e","tid":1027912,"uid":90890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:24:10.000Z","msg":"未入都估到係呢單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d295ad1cd70c71af9d938d5cf04dc7dc3863be","tid":1027912,"uid":55851,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"74ea7537f62e9f248d0b154e14a560b3546f7d3e",